## ✅ ConfirmDialog Component Usage

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Type Selection

**MUST use correct type for each scenario:**

```typescript
// Delete confirmation
<ConfirmDialog
  type="danger"
  title="삭제 확인"
  message="정말로 삭제하시겠습니까?"
  confirmText="삭제"
  cancelText="취소"
  onConfirm={handleDelete}
  onCancel={handleCancel}
/>

// Warning message
<ConfirmDialog
  type="warning"
  title="알림"
  message="이 작업은 되돌릴 수 없습니다."
  onConfirm={handleConfirm}
  onCancel={handleCancel}
/>

// Success message (after create/update) - CRITICAL
<ConfirmDialog
  type="success" // ✅ REQUIRED for success messages
  title="등록 완료"
  message="정상적으로 등록되었습니다."
  confirmText="확인"
  onConfirm={handleClose}
  onCancel={handleClose}
/>
```

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Use `type="danger"` for success messages
- ❌ Use `type="success"` for delete confirmations
- ❌ Mix up `onConfirm` and `onCancel` handlers
- ❌ Use ConfirmDialog for complex content (use Modal component instead)

### Success Message Pattern (CRITICAL)

**MUST ALWAYS use `type="success"` for:**

- ✅ Registration (등록) completion
- ✅ Update (수정) completion
- ✅ Any successful operation notification

**MUST follow this pattern:**

```typescript
if (response.resultCode === "00" || response.result === "00") {
  setMessageDialogTitle("등록 완료");
  setMessageDialogMessage(
    response.resultMessage || "정상적으로 등록되었습니다."
  );
  setMessageDialogType("success"); // ✅ REQUIRED - must be "success"
  setShowMessageDialog(true);
}
```

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Use `type="danger"` or `type="warning"` for success messages
- ❌ Skip type specification (defaults to "danger" which is wrong for success)

**Reference Implementation:**

- ✅ Check `src/features/adminWeb/program/list/ui/ProgramListPageView.tsx` for success message pattern

