## 🔍 Prevention Checklist

**MUST verify ALL items before implementing form submission error handling:**

- [ ] **Checked existing registration forms** (`MemberRegisterForm`, `BoardRegisterForm`, `ProgramRegisterForm`)
- [ ] **Using ConfirmDialog ONLY** for API communication errors (no red text)
- [ ] **Using `type="danger"`** for API errors (NOT "error")
- [ ] **Error state (`error`) is initialized** but not used for API errors
- [ ] **ConfirmDialog is properly configured** with title, message, type, and handlers
- [ ] **No `setError()` calls** in API error catch blocks
- [ ] **No red text display** in component for API errors
- [ ] **Console.error is used** for debugging API errors
- [ ] **`setLoading(false)` is in `finally` block** for proper cleanup

