## 💡 Key Principles

1. **Consistency First**: All admin registration/edit forms MUST follow the same error handling pattern
2. **User Experience**: ConfirmDialog is more visible and user-friendly than red text
3. **Maintainability**: Consistent patterns make code easier to maintain and update
4. **Pattern Verification**: Always check existing forms before implementing new error handling

