## 🎨 Custom Inline Modal Pattern

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Required Structure

**MUST follow this exact structure when creating custom inline modals:**

```tsx
{
  showModal && (
    <>
      {/* Overlay - MUST */}
      <div
        className="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 z-50"
        onClick={handleCloseModal}
      ></div>

      {/* Modal Container - MUST */}
      <div className="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-50 p-4">
        <div
          className="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-2xl max-h-[80vh] flex flex-col overflow-hidden"
          onClick={(e) => e.stopPropagation()}
        >
          {/* Header - MUST */}
          <div className="p-4 border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 flex justify-between items-center rounded-t-lg">
            <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Modal Title</h2>
            <button
              onClick={handleCloseModal}
              className="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 text-2xl font-bold leading-none"
              aria-label="닫기"
            >
              ×
            </button>
          </div>

          {/* Content - MUST */}
          <div className="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 rounded-b-lg">
            {/* Your content here */}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </>
  );
}
```

### Styling Requirements (CRITICAL)

**MUST:**

- ✅ Use `rounded-lg` for main container (NOT `rounded-xl` or other values)
- ✅ Use `overflow-hidden` on main container (preserves rounded corners)
- ✅ Use `rounded-t-lg` on header
- ✅ Use `rounded-b-lg` on content area
- ✅ Use `z-50` for both overlay and modal (consistent z-index)
- ✅ Use `bg-black bg-opacity-50` for overlay
- ✅ Use `shadow-lg` for modal container
- ✅ Use `stopPropagation` on modal content to prevent overlay click

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Use `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`, or other border radius values (inconsistent)
- ❌ Forget `overflow-hidden` (breaks rounded corners appearance)
- ❌ Use different z-index values (must be `z-50`)
- ❌ Skip `stopPropagation` on modal content (causes modal to close when clicking inside)
- ❌ Use different overlay colors or opacity

### Size Guidelines

**MUST use appropriate max-width and max-height:**

| Content Type    | Max Width   | Max Height     |
| --------------- | ----------- | -------------- |
| Small selection | `max-w-2xl` | `max-h-[80vh]` |
| Medium content  | `max-w-4xl` | `max-h-[90vh]` |
| Large content   | `max-w-6xl` | `max-h-[90vh]` |

**Reference Implementation:**

- ✅ `src/features/adminWeb/menu/tree/ui/MenuTreePageView.tsx` - Custom inline modals for menu selection and program search

