## ♿ Accessibility Requirements

### ⚠️ CRITICAL: Keyboard Support

**MUST:**

- ✅ Support ESC key to close (Modal component handles this automatically)
- ✅ Support Tab navigation within modal
- ✅ Trap focus within modal when open
- ✅ Return focus to trigger element when closed

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Allow focus to escape modal
- ❌ Skip keyboard navigation support
- ❌ Forget ESC key handler in custom modals

### ARIA Attributes

**MUST:**

```tsx
<button
  onClick={onClose}
  aria-label="닫기" // ✅ Required for close buttons
>
  ×
</button>
```

### Screen Reader Support

**MUST:**

- ✅ Provide descriptive titles
- ✅ Use semantic HTML (buttons, headings)
- ✅ Announce modal state changes

