## ❌ Common Mistakes

### Mistake 1: Wrong Component Selection

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
// Using ConfirmDialog for complex content
<ConfirmDialog
  isOpen={showForm}
  message={<ComplexForm />} // ❌ Too complex for ConfirmDialog
/>
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
<Modal isOpen={showForm} title="Form Title" onClose={onClose}>
  <ComplexForm />
</Modal>
```

### Mistake 2: Missing Overflow Handling

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
<div className="bg-white rounded-lg">
  {/* Long content without overflow handling */}
</div>
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
<div className="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
  <div className="overflow-y-auto max-h-[80vh]">{/* Long content */}</div>
</div>
```

### Mistake 3: Incorrect CSS Classes

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
<Modal>
  <div className="dialog-container">
    {" "}
    {/* ❌ Wrong class */}
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</Modal>
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
<Modal>
  {/* Modal component handles container classes automatically */}
  <div>{/* content */}</div>
</Modal>
```

### Mistake 4: Missing State Cleanup

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
const handleCloseModal = () => {
  setIsModalOpen(false);
  // ❌ Forgot to reset form data
};
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
const handleCloseModal = () => {
  setIsModalOpen(false);
  setFormData(initialFormData); // ✅ Reset state
  setErrors({}); // ✅ Clear errors
};
```

### Mistake 5: Z-Index Conflicts

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
<div className="fixed z-10">
  {" "}
  {/* ❌ Too low */}
  {/* modal */}
</div>
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
<div className="fixed z-50">
  {" "}
  {/* ✅ Standard z-index */}
  {/* modal */}
</div>
```

### Mistake 6: Wrong Success Message Type

**❌ WRONG:**

```typescript
// Using danger type for success
if (response.resultCode === "00") {
  setMessageDialogType("danger"); // ❌ Wrong type
  setShowMessageDialog(true);
}
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```typescript
if (response.resultCode === "00") {
  setMessageDialogType("success"); // ✅ Correct type
  setShowMessageDialog(true);
}
```

### Mistake 7: Inconsistent Border Radius

**❌ WRONG:**

```tsx
<div className="rounded-xl"> {/* ❌ Inconsistent */}
```

**✅ CORRECT:**

```tsx
<div className="rounded-lg"> {/* ✅ Standard */}
```

